# Learnings

Reusable takeaways captured from ticket retrospectives — patterns worth applying
proactively on future tickets, not just noted once and forgotten.

## How this file grows

At the end of any skill's Retrospective step, if a takeaway describes a
**reusable pattern** (would help on a *different* ticket, not just this one),
append it below as one line under the right heading. Ticket-specific notes
stay in the PR description — they do not belong here.

Keep entries terse (one line, imperative or observational). If an entry is
superseded or contradicted by a later one, remove the stale entry instead of
stacking both.

